{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b1835c1435","title":"望杨罗耿部弃敌十六军一部","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8776f11699","index":0,"year":1948,"month":10,"day":13,"articleId":"b1835c1435"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"77ba48e561","type":"paragraph","text":"望杨罗耿部弃敌十六军一部”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"b1835c1435"},{"id":"46e116032f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年10月13日）杨、罗、耿（一）你们攻克西拨子、盆道、青龙桥、八达岭等处，齐敌一部，并准备在一周内彻底破坏怀来、北平段铁路线，甚好。（二）为吸引九十二军一个师（已由北平附近开塘沽）回顾，不去增援葫芦岛，为吸引三十五军继续向东，以利杨李李而在绥远行动之目的，望你们于破路之同时，集结相当兵力歼灭十六军一二个团","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"b1835c1435"},{"id":"2a6d90578b","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"b1835c1435"},{"id":"20cfccc962","type":"paragraph","text":"十三日十五时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给华北军区第二兵团司令员杨得志、政治委员罗瑞和参谋长球题的屯报。[2]杨李李，招杨成武、李井泉、李天燥，当时分别任华北军区第三兵","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"b1835c1435"}],"page":{"id":"decd64485a","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"b1835c1435","start":46,"end":46}}}},"__N_SSG":true}